text: Taworn Tarwan (born 9 September 1947) is a Thai former cyclist. He competed at the 1972 Summer Olympics and 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Thai male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Thailand Category:Cyclists at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Cyclists at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
